      <xref linkend="libxext"/> and
      <xref linkend="libxfixes"/> (for X11 API support), and
      <xref linkend="mesa"/> (for GLX and EGL API support)
    </para>

    <note><para>
      There is a circular dependency between mesa and this package. If you need
      the VAAPI driver provided by mesa, build this package without EGL and GLX
      support, install mesa, then reinstall this package with EGL and GLX support.
    </para></note>

